If you need it MORE QUICKLY please email sales@modudesigns.com before you make payment.


If your confused have any questions, send an email and we are more than happy to help.

100% Nylon reversible lining, one side black and reverse side camouflage print. Available in 4 colourways (Blue Camo, Orange Camo, Pink Camo & Green Camo)

• Insulated 100% Polyester filing 
• Heavy duty Brass Zip with MODU 4 triangles.
